  "description": "A long, sweeping view of the Golden Gate Bridge extending across a wide, sparkling blue bay. The bridge is a warm orange-red, contrasting with the cool tones of the water and the hilly, green landscape on either side. Gentle waves create a shimmering texture on the water's surface. Distant hills and headlands fade into the misty background, suggesting depth and atmospheric perspective. A tiny sailboat is visible on the lower left, providing a sense of scale. The overall composition is panoramic and serene.",
